            <!-- Editions, Translations, and Relevant Publications -->
            <noteGrp type="publications">
               <note type="editions">A critical edition by Denis Gril was printed alongside his French translation in Le Dévoilement des Effets du Voyage (Paris, 1994). This did not have access to the holograph (Yusuf Ağa 4859). An amended edition, based on the Gril’s work but including Yusuf Ağa 4859, plus a translation into Urdu, has been published by the Ibn ʿArabī Foundation (Rawalpindi, Pakistan. 2013). Ed. Abrār Aḥmad Shāhī Critical edition by ʿAbd al-ʿAzīz al-Manṣūb, based on mss. from the MIAS archive. Published by al-Qudus, Cairo, 2018.</note>
               <note type="translations">English translation by Angla Jaffray: The Secrets of Journeying, Anqa Publishing, Oxford, 2015. French translation by Denis Gril: Le Dévoilement des Effets du Voyage, Paris 1994</note>
